    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels brand new. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always kept it garaged, and the interior still has that fresh smell. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe how clean it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
