      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that has lived its entire life in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the premium leather remains incredibly supple and carries that distinct showroom aroma, with absolutely no bolster wear or sun-fading on the dashboard. Every switch and button functions with factory-fresh tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is meticulously detailed, showing no signs of grime, corrosion, or leaks. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive, chronological service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians. This is a rare, time-capsule opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
