      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute dream of a car, and let me tell you, it is stunning. It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or dent to be found. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
